                <head>135. [Editorial Note]</head>
                <note rend="inline">A document numbering error has been identified in <hi
                        rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1964–1968, Volume XXX, China: The
                    printed volume skips from document 134 to 136. This has been noted in the online
                    errata, but printed volumes have not been revised.</note>
